"D-arker Extermination V":
"You're proving to be rather ambitious as far as
ARKS ops go, so maybe this request is right up
your alley. I want you to destroy any and all large
D-arkers you encounter. You choose where.
This shouldn't be impossible for you, based on
your performance so far. But it's up to you
whether or not you want to do it. No one is
forcing you to do anything.

*Target: Hostiles level 16 or higher"

"あんたはそれなりにやる気のある
アークスみたいだから
一つ、この依頼を受けてはみないかい？
大型のダーカーを狙っての殲滅。
場所は問わない。
あんたの力なら、不可能じゃないはずだ。
やるやらないは任せるけどさ。

※Lv.16～のエネミーが対象"
